# Naming Convention

## Directories (locked)

All directories use **lowercase kebab-case**. No exceptions.

- ✅ `src/components/`, `docs/legal/drafts/`, `docs/legal/executed/change-orders/`
- ❌ `Drafts/`, `Change_Orders/`, `MSAs/`

### Per-document ID folders

Per-document folders under `docs/legal/` that are named after a document ID retain uppercase in the ID portion only:

- ✅ `docs/legal/drafts/sows/SOW-0001/`
- ✅ `docs/legal/drafts/acceptance/AC-0001/`
- ❌ `docs/legal/drafts/SOWs/SOW-0001/`

## Files

- **Code files** (`.ts`, `.tsx`, `.js`, `.css`, etc.): lowercase kebab-case — `server-functions.ts`, `card.tsx`
  - Exception: PascalCase component files are acceptable when matching the exported component name — `Hero.tsx`, `ContactFormEmail.tsx`
- **Legal documents** (`.md` under `docs/legal/`): Title Case with spaces — `SOW-0001 - Statement of Work - RAD X Website.md`
- **Config/tooling** (`.json`, `.mjs`, etc.): lowercase kebab-case — `package.json`, `generate-image-variants.mjs`
